constructcovf           Construct usual fractional covariance functions
constructgrid           Construct usual grids on some specific
                        manifolds
fieldsim                Simulate manifold indexed Gaussian field by the
                        fieldsim method
manifold-class          Manifold class
quadvar                 Estimate the Hurst parameter of a plane indexed
                        fractional Brownian field by the quadratic
                        variations method
setManifold             Set a S4 manifold object
visualize               Visualize some of specific manifold indexed
                        fractional Gaussian process
